CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 8, 2013

[Cite as 05/08/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-Ohio-1857.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2012- 0745. Zeune v. Bender.

In Mandamus. On motions to dismiss. Motions granted. Motion for judgment on the pleadings denied as moot. Cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Pfeifer, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, Kennedy, French, and O’Neill, JJ., concur.
